{"tid":1467330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你班撚屌前線同和你飛跟住郁手前用下腦先啦","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:13:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:26:07.000Z","uid":1915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"aca2a2ef5485f5cefb0b51996ccfb9246de3214c","tid":1467330,"uid":1915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:13:11.000Z","msg":"首先不割不分！<br />\n但不論今日帶頭私了既係人係鬼<br />\n同有份私了既人係邊派都好<br />\n我地真係未夠成熟<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">還眼唔係得個講字 </span><br />\n以眼還眼係咩意思呀<br />\n就係敵人點對你地就點對番敵人<br />\n我地只係要學足啲<br />\n共狗最撚叻<span style=\"color: red;\">枱面交戲枱底郁手</span><br />\n復仇都要冷靜<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係要鏡頭前直播打爆人眼<br />\n係要敵人雙眼入巷單眼出<br />\n私了既野唔應該係國際舞台出現</span></span><br />\n<br />\n出面果班屌自己人同警犬有乜分別既全部都係痴線<br />\n執法系統已經失效既社會仲講唔好變成佢地<br />\n咁公義由邊個去彰顯？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">枱面和你飛 枱底私了</span></span>"},{"pid":"8396864334c349064a18507c687752bc7c9208c8","tid":1467330,"uid":1915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:16:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">以眼還眼</span></span>"},{"pid":"54fb1a8e887f48d21b64a0d40db5ebc0609c899f","tid":1467330,"uid":1915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:16:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">以眼還眼</span></span>"},{"pid":"d616abc5f1e750abdfed193fab5f9ceee525c901","tid":1467330,"uid":1915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:18:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">以眼還眼</span></span>"},{"pid":"1e7e89159dcf9d2ee0836a59043690647742ad9a","tid":1467330,"uid":1915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:19:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">暗巷私了</span></span>"},{"pid":"2770edd0233484978eba948c5c01e7af9361b3d4","tid":1467330,"ui